{"tid":292004,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［一人一個］不一樣的關西之旅","createTime":"2017-06-21T04:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T10:37:44.000Z","uid":70337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8762de208467c0520ca0db7642d21bd7faf99ad","tid":292004,"uid":70337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"去過大阪兩次，黎緊去第三次，有時都會睇下呢度嘅巴絲plan嘅行程，但京阪神入面啲咩寺咩城咩社咩山好多都去過，所以就開個post交流下，大家有無去過啲偏門、未有好多人發掘嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋個磚先，plan緊其中兩個地方好似都比較少人講（講過唔好打我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n第一個係京都 天橋立，話係日本三景之一<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/115711_5eaa20e1511604ba0d68271090a525ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F115711_5eaa20e1511604ba0d68271090a525ac.jpg&h=97ba1edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二個係都係係京都, 美山地區<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/115657_0f8d275da2695c141ae709568394577f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F115657_0f8d275da2695c141ae709568394577f.jpg&h=eed5f496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸啲圖google搵，詳情未去過講唔到好多，仲有啲比較少人講嘅有滋賀琵琶湖白鬚鳥居、神戶六甲山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313d081d8956b31a53e7af715878275e8d2a73f8","tid":292004,"uid":70337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T07:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68ac75ae4660a919173065525f94bcf42c78ae1","tid":292004,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:05:12.000Z","msg":"之前咪有個post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要個到都列左幾多偏地方"},{"pid":"af0d7a0a5bcd98d10bebc14f899f395aa11f0302","tid":292004,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"天橋立真心麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為之前去咗宮島松島先諗住去埋<br />\n<br />\n反而那智瀑布，伊勢神宮就可以一去"},{"pid":"14c2ce760d11a7523dd3087c29b4402e7464db69","tid":292004,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"仲以為係乜添<br />\n<br />\n比少少驚喜我ok?"},{"pid":"d576baf4209efb1fab4d113e517eae5b56ecbfe4","tid":292004,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"熊野3山推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔多 好舒服<br />\n<br />\n上年8月尾去完"},{"pid":"af92f8643a623d2c63ab5a3b4d3f90bb35dfd396","tid":292004,"uid":70337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前咪有個post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要個到都列左幾多偏地方</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來之前有post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我無留意到<br />\n有無link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係個台拉左幾頁都搵唔到"},{"pid":"95ec9d44bb90179b73e3891536bb17e12bc6af29","tid":292004,"uid":70337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為係乜添<br />\n<br />\n比少少驚喜我ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想有驚喜呀"},{"pid":"47c2dc4536c5e3ebc82c50323b69141ca4df4727","tid":292004,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"下次我想去睇寶塚歌劇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00ec97300d272ce67b3f507ed33ad8937f0036f","tid":292004,"uid":55570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:14:10.000Z","msg":"琵琶湖去山頂cafe 之後去白鬚神社 有時間可去埋浮御堂"},{"pid":"908e1a614c6eecf5f9eb6d5d9795abc74c8a366e","tid":292004,"uid":70337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<br />\n行程問題天橋立skip<br />\n但決定去美山"},{"pid":"3ead79ab3aee6a684bbc52b98fb52aee9e9937bb","tid":292004,"uid":70337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琵琶湖去山頂cafe 之後去白鬚神社 有時間可去埋浮御堂</blockquote><br />\n呢個會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打覺得白鬚神社個邊可以逛幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}